e%2C%20and%20accountant%20Richard%20Kahn%20as%20his%20estate%20executors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20older%20versions%20of%20Epstein's%20will%20were%20released%20following%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-files-release-live-updates-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEpstein%20Files%20Transparency%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20required%20the%20Justice%20Department%20to%20make%20its%20Epstein-related%20files%20public.%20In%20addition%20to%20Epstein's%202019%20indictment%2C%20his%20associate%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20was%20sentenced%20to%2020%20years%20in%20prison%20in%202021%20for%20trafficking%20girls%20to%20him%2C%20and%20in%202008%2C%20he%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20a%20crime%20involving%20sexual%20misconduct%20with%20a%20minor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20files%20include%20references%20to%20many%20of%20Epstein's%20powerful%20associates%2C%20including%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-files-celebrities-photos-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Bill%20Clinton%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Inclusion%20in%20the%20documents%20isn't%20an%20indication%20of%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECayne%2C%20who%20died%20in%202021%2C%20was%20listed%20as%20a%20co-executor%20for%20Epstein's%20estate%20in%20versions%20of%20Epstein's%20will%20signed%20in%202003%20and%202004.%20Epstein%20worked%20at%20Bear%20Stearns%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20before%20becoming%20a%20financial%20advisor%20to%20billionaires%20Les%20Wexner%20and%20Leon%20Black.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECayne's%20daughter%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20Epstein%20listed%20Staley%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20then%20an%20executive%20at%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20backup%20executor%20to%20his%20will.%20In%202013%2C%20Staley%20was%20promoted%20to%20co-executor%20status%2C%20alongside%20Indyke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaley%20kept%20the%20position%20as%20co-executor%20of%20Epstein's%20will%20in%20the%202014%20version%20as%20well.%20By%20then%2C%20Epstein%20had%20listed%20Summers%20as%20a%20backup%20executor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20attorney%20for%20Staley%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20Staley%20said%20in%20a%202019%20letter%20to%20a%20UK%20regulator%20that%20he%20did%20not%20have%20a%20close%20relationship%20with%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaley%20stepped%20down%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20Barclays%20in%202021%20following%20an%20investigation%20into%20his%20ties%20with%20Epstein%20from%20the%20British%20bank%20regulator%2C%20which%20banned%20him%20from%20working%20in%20the%20financial%20industry.%20A%20UK%20court%20earlier%20this%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjes-staley-barclays-ceo-financial-services-ban-upheld-jeffrey-epstein-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eupheld%20Staley's%20ban%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20finding%20that%20he%20lied%20about%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Bpurely%20professional%26quot%3B%20relationship%20with%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESummers%20stepped%20down%20from%20his%20teaching%20post%20at%20Harvard%20and%20from%20his%20board%20seat%20at%20OpenAI%20following%20the%20release%20of%20numerous%20emails%20between%20him%20and%20Epstein%20by%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20Goldberg%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Summers%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20economist%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20Epstein's%20financial%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Summers%20had%20absolutely%20no%20knowledge%20that%20he%20was%20included%20in%20an%20early%20version%20of%20Epstein's%20will%20and%20had%20no%20involvement%20in%20his%20financial%20matters%20or%20the%20administration%20of%20his%20estate%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldberg%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpstein%20also%20included%20another%20prominent%20figure%20in%20the%20penultimate%20version%20of%20his%20will.%20A%20draft%20of%20the%20will%2C%20released%20by%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20listed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-emails-goldman-sachs-kathryn-ruemmler-attorney-client-privilege-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etop%20Goldman%20Sachs%20lawyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20Kathryn%20Ruemmler%20as%20the%20backup%20estate%20executor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERuemmler%2C%20through%20JPMorgan%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20when%20the%20will%20was%20released%20by%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-will-estate-wall-street-executives-executors-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766539556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694b1e0004eda4732f2e131a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-will-estate-wall-street-executives-executors-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jeffrey%20Epstein's%20wills%20named%20figures%20like%20Larry%20Summers%20and%20Jes%20Staley%20as%20possible%20executors%2C%20DOJ%20files%20show.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-will-estate-wall-street-executives-executors-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rivalries%20and%20rumours%3A%20How%20the%20new%20order%20of%20the%20Murdoch%20dynasty%20is%20playing%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766539513000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fbece%2Flive%2F04dfd140-d9cf-11f0-a8dc-93c15fe68710.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fart