m%20and%20others%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bce91c7-c7a8-4205-bc0c-fd12ddbc041c%5C%22%3EDespite%20his%20successful%20investments%2C%20he%20still%20has%20one%20regret%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20Schultz%20said%20he%20spends%20most%20of%20his%20free%20time%20exercising%20and%20working%20on%20his%20podcast%20and%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20%26quot%3BLottery%2C%20Dreams%2C%20and%20Fortune%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20highlights%20the%20story%20of%20other%20lottery%20winners.%20%26quot%3BYouTube%20brings%20in%20some%20money%2C%20but%20I%20can%20live%20off%20my%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20making%20great%20investment%20choices%2C%20Schultz%20still%20regrets%20overlooking%20one%20specific%20investment.%26quot%3BI%20wish%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-buy-bitcoin-hyper%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20had%20invested%20in%20bitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20that's%20my%20only%20regret%20about%20how%20I've%20spent%20the%20winnings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Shultz's%20initial%20decision%20to%20seek%20professional%20financial%20help%20set%20him%20up%20for%20years%20of%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ECorrection%3A%20December%2023%2C%202025%20%E2%80%94An%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20story%20misstated%20the%20details%20of%20the%20next%20Powerball%20drawing.%20It%20is%20for%20%241.7%20billion%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-powerball-winner-how-spent-lottery-winnings-avoided-broke-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766529151000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694af45804eda4732f2e1076%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-powerball-winner-how