%3E'Stranger%20Things%3A%20The%20First%20Shadow'%20is%20a%20prequel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20First%20Shadow%26quot%3B%20is%20set%20in%201959%2C%20about%2024%20years%20before%20the%20events%20of%20season%20one%20in%201983%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20older%20characters%20from%20the%20TV%20show%2C%20including%20Joyce%20Byers%2C%20Jim%20Hopper%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstranger-things-deaths-ranked-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20late%20Bob%20Newby%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20students%20at%20Hawkins%20High%20in%20Indiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20play%20largely%20focuses%20on%20a%20new%20student%20at%20the%20school%2C%20Henry%20Creel%2C%20whom%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstranger-things-vecna-reveal-made-me-love-the-show-again-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%20kids%20refer%20to%20as%20Vecna%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20season%20four%20of%20the%20Netflix%20series%2C%20Henry%2FVecna%20is%20established%20as%20the%20primary%20villain%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sort%20of%20dark%20wizard%20residing%20in%20the%20Upside%20Down%20who%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20command%20its%20monsters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20series%20of%20flashbacks%2C%20it's%20revealed%20that%20Henry%20was%20once%20a%20regular%20human%20kid%20with%20secret%20magical%20powers.%20After%20the%20Creels%20moved%20to%20Hawkins%20in%201959%2C%20Henry%20began%20using%20his%20powers%20to%20psychologically%20torture%20his%20family%2C%20eventually%20murdering%20his%20mother%20and%20sister.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jamie%20Campbell%20Bower%20as%20Henry%20and%20Millie%20Bobby%20Brown%20as%20Eleven%20in%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%20season%20four.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6949952104eda4732f2dfbce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221914%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJamie%20Campbell%20Bower%20as%20Henry%20and%20Millie%20Bobby%20Brown%20as%20Eleven%20in%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%20season%20four.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Netflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20Henry%20was%20brought%20to%20Hawkins%20Lab%2C%20where%20he%20became%20the%20first%20subject%20in%20Dr.%20Martin%20Brenner's%20psychokinetic%20experiments.%20Over%20time%2C%20Brenner%20grew%20fearful%20of%20Henry%2C%20so%20he%20installed%20a%20device%20in%20Henry's%20neck%20that%20tracked%20and%20subdued%20him.%20He%20also%20used%20Henry's%20blood%20to%20create%20more%20child%20subjects%2C%20including%20Eleven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201979%2C%20a%20grown-up%20Henry%20tricked%20a%20young%20Eleven%20into%20removing%20the%20device.%20With%20his%20powers%20restored%2C%20he%20slaughtered%20most%20of%20the%20scientists%2C%20orderlies%2C%20and%20children%20in%20the%20lab.%20After%20a%20brief%20standoff%2C%20Eleven%20managed%20to%20overpower%20Henry%2C%20accidentally%20opening%20an%20inter-dimensional%20gate%20and%20forcing%20him%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%2C%26quot%3B%20Henry%20tells%20Eleven%20that%20he%20sees%20humans%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bunique%20type%20of%20pest%26quot%3B%20and%20resents%20the%20structure%20of%20everyday%20life%2C%20which%20motivates%20him%20to%20commit%20murder.%20(%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20just%20waiting.%20Waiting%20for%20it%20all%20to%20be%20over.%20All%20while%20performing%20in%20a%20silly%2C%20terrible%20play.%26quot%3B)%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20show%20does%20not%20explain%20how%20he%20came%20to%20be%20this%20way%3B%20instead%2C%20it%20presents%20him%20as%20a%20natural-born%20predator%2C%20pure%20evil%20embodied.%20By%20contrast%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20First%20Shadow%26quot%3B%20humanizes%20Henry%2C%20creating%20a%20richer%20backstory%20for%20the%20boy%20who%20grew%20up%20to%20terrorize%20Hawkins.%20It%20also%20explains%20how%20Henry%20got%20his%20powers%20in%20the%20first%20plac