ed%20up%20to%20be%20a%20recess%20monitor%20at%20my%20daughter's%20school%20(I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20fun%20to%20see%20her%20at%20recess%20and%20get%20some%20fresh%20air%2C%20but%20I'll%20report%20back%20on%20that%20after%20I%20actually%20do%20it!).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Saturday%2C%20I%20worked%20my%20first%20shift%20at%20the%20library%2C%20and%20I%20%3Cem%3Eloved%3C%2Fem%3E%20it.%20It%20doesn't%20pay%20very%20much%2C%20but%20I%20loved%20having%20a%20reason%20to%20get%20dressed%20and%20do%20my%20hair%2C%20the%20peace%20and%20quiet%20of%20a%20library%20on%20a%20winter%20afternoon%2C%20and%20the%20simple%20satisfaction%20of%20helping%20people%20find%20their%20next%20great%20read.%20I%20had%20an%20absolute%20blast%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20even%20remarked%20that%20I%20was%20'jovial'%20when%20I%20got%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20exploring%20some%20other%20business%20ideas%20that%20have%20been%20on%20the%20back%20burner%2C%20based%20on%20things%20I%20enjoy%2C%20such%20as%20self-publishing%20fiction%20books%20on%20Amazon%2C%20becoming%20certified%20as%20a%20personal%20trainer%2C%20or%20expanding%20the%20small%20farm%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20it's%20a%20time%20to%20explore%20what%20the%20next%20part%20of%20my%20life%20looks%20like.%20I'm%20feeling%20that%20sort%20of%20restlessness%20that%20only%20a%20mother%20in%20the%20throes%20of%20perimenopause%20who%20has%20dedicated%20nearly%20two%20decades%20of%20her%20life%20to%20others%20can%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-facing-money-fears-and-middle-age-transition-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766506621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693826ec71107c9f34579395%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-facing-money-fears-and-middle-age-transition-2025-12%22%2C%22su