0him%20the%20RG%20Samsara%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20activism%20is%20important%2C%20this%20biologist%20believes%20in%20shedding%20an%20equal%20spotlight%20on%20creating%20impact%20through%20policy%20frameworks.%20As%20Chair%20of%20the%20Asian%20Elephant%20Specialist%20Group%20for%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature)%20for%20the%20past%2012%20years%2C%20Menon%20elaborates%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20work%20in%20advising%20various%20governments%20on%20%E2%80%9Cdoing%20things%20right%20for%20elephants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20includes%20bringing%20out%20scientific%20work%2C%20guidelines%2C%20and%20manuals.%20It%20also%20includes%20planning%20linear%20infrastructure%3B%20highways%2C%20railways%2C%20road%20passes%2C%20and%20power%20lines%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20the%20elephants%20are%20allowed%20to%20pass%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20segues%20into%20the%20topic%20of%20identifying%20and%20protecting%20elephant%20corridors%2C%20a%20brainchild%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20overarching%20goal%20being%20to%20secure%20a%20%E2%80%98rite%20of%20passage%E2%80%99%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F188598%2Felephant-doctor-assam-treats-hundreds-wildlife-hero-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20mammals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20WTI%20along%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20top%20scientists%20have%20identified%20and%20surveyed%20101%20such%20functional%20corridors%20across%2011%20states%20for%20the%2029%2C000%20odd%20Asian%20Elephants%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20a%20spare%20bedroom%20project%20to%20a%20phenomenal%20trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202023%20study%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Wildlife%20and%20Biodiversity%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20corri